data.description: Your dream home is waiting for you! Come see this beautiful one of a kind end unit conveniently located in Flowery Branch. The kitchen opens up into the family room, and is ready for cooking with plenty of counter space and cabinets for storage. The main living area features a double-sided fire place and plenty of natural light that ads a touch of freshness to the interiors. Walk upstairs to the master suite that easily accommodates a king-size bed and additional furniture. The two additional bedrooms provides versatility for a home office, guests or a growing family. This is a must see! Hurry... This home won't last! Close proximity to the freeway, dinning, shopping and entertainment.       HVAC replaced August 2023.
